---
title: Mini Chicken Thigh Caesar Wraps with Spiced Potato Rounds
description: All the flavours of a classic chicken Caesar, but in quick, fuss-free handhelds! Crisp spinach and tomato are the base for creamy, cheesy dressing and steak-spiced baked chicken.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mini-chicken-thigh-caesar-wraps-f04e56ee.jpg
